				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Soloing the Neriad Shaw<a name="33559"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 8 04 10:12 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Soloing the Shawl is not so much a question of gear as it is skill.  The toughest part now is getting down there with the zone changes.  The soloing part is easy.  Set up on top of the well where you have the sirens NOT in the water.  Target the named, start singing charm, when charm is almost done casting jump in the water and when it lands jump back out.  You want to keep charming the named so she takes the most dmg.  Do this over and over until they are all dead.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
