From what I've seen they can spawn anywhere a Neriad can. The most accessable ones being the 5 spawns under the siren temple with Mistress Latazura and the circular tunnel area behind it down the alternating ramps (hard to explain in words but if you know the area you should know where I mean). This is the area where I got mine.</span></td>
