				<td colspan="2"><span>This was a real nasty camp for adds.  All in after 4 days and 5 deaths...4 deaths due to stuck bug causing fade to fail and 5 mobs to rape me, (another story).
<br />

<br />
The 3rd sea princess killed dropped the shawl.  I was never so glad to leave this h*ll hole.  Soloed with the best bet bieng the damage shield mele combo..and if many mobs I went the charm pet routine finishing with damage shield mele.
<br />

<br />
sang marr, veshan,warsong, and ...Not muse used the uber slow/snare. these things flee, and yer dead when they run and bring 6 adds.(stuck bug makes that real bad)
<br />
had charm and morrel memmed with divine arua in case i needed to flee. invis too.  oh DA does not work if your stuck in the wall (freaking bug, did i mention the bug)  
<br />

<br />
I camped mostly down the ramp from the mistress in the pool, swam there from the well and went all the way south then made a left and went to the pool/ramp.
<br />

<br />
Lessons learned from this camp,  firstly the sea princess summons, and will follow you on land. She does not see invis.  I killed her on the land ramp outa the water.
<br />

<br />
2nd you better have a snare memed or you will die.  adds were insane.
<br />

<br />
3rd if you panic you die. remember all the things charm kiting taught you and don't panic. Once broken kill one at a time.  I got cocky and used a pet alot of the time, this has risks though.
<br />

<br />
Moose 
