				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Soloing the Neriad Shaw<a name="46191"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 15 04 3:22 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>After like 2 months of off and on killing in SG i FINALLY got my shawl June 12th, 2004. I did NOT solo this time, i had 2 other bards with me and a cleric. After the first spawn in the back where the 5 spawns are, a neriad sea princess spawned and dropped mine. Now, only one bard still needed the shawl. The next spawn another princess spawned and didnt drop nothin, but on the 3rd spawn it dropped after another princess poped. Total time there was about 1 hr 10 min. 
<br />

<br />
Im not sure if they fixed the drop rate/spawn rate because the princesses have been spawning a ton and now dropping the shawl more often for me. 
<br />

<br />
Another side note, the next day i took another bard friend to SG and we had a princess up already and he dropped it. Total time that night was about 15 min. This time it was just him and i played my cleric.
<br />

<br />
Gl to all and hopefully you will have it drop soon enough <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> </span></td>
